name: your future is an algorithm
description: processed image still taken from a multiprocessed video file - originally created as reference for a (2016) 200 x 150 cm canvas commission [the canvas was eventually destroyed] - this is a work that continues to pose not only the familiar question of 'what is art?' but additionally challenges the notion of 'who' or 'what' is the 'artist' - technology is changing our conceptual understanding of reality day by day | Brendan Conrad Forde | @acid_very
